      <title>欧盟边境争端导致贸易陷入困境，损失数百万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/romania-and-bulgaria-join-schengen-as-trucks-wait-at-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚和保加利亚将于 3 月 31 日加入欧盟申根区，但加入的公路路线是其贸易的命脉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/romania-and-bulgaria-join-schengen-as-trucks-wait-at-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 05:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
