    <item>
      <title>国安法通过后美国将限制香港官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/us-to-set-curbs-on-hk-officials-after-city-passes-security-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在香港快速通过国内安全立法后，美国将对一些香港官员实施新的签证限制，华盛顿称该立法限制了全球金融中心的公开讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/us-to-set-curbs-on-hk-officials-after-city-passes-security-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 03:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上诉法院表示，Meta 不能推迟 FTC 对隐私条款的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/meta-can-t-delay-ftc-review-of-privacy-terms-appeals-court-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 未能说服联邦上诉法院推迟美国联邦贸易委员会对其 Facebook 部门涉嫌侵犯隐私的行为进行重新审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/meta-can-t-delay-ftc-review-of-privacy-terms-appeals-court-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 00:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着全球救助计划的形成，国际货币基金组织批准向埃及提供 80 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/imf-approves-8-billion-egypt-loan-as-global-bailout-takes-shape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织批准向埃及增加 50 亿美元的贷款计划，这是全球援助浪潮的一部分，承诺支持因加沙战争而承受更大压力的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/imf-approves-8-billion-egypt-loan-as-global-bailout-takes-shape</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 22:23:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将访问巴尔的摩，工作人员准备清理倒塌的桥梁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/biden-to-visit-baltimore-as-crews-prepare-to-clear-fallen-bridge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他将于下周前往巴尔的摩，美国寻求加快清理和重建倒塌的弗朗西斯·斯科特基大桥的紧急工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/biden-to-visit-baltimore-as-crews-prepare-to-clear-fallen-bridge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 18:48:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳森的辞职将引发关于双重身份和权力共享的新问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-29/donaldson-resignation-will-prompt-fresh-questions-for-dup-and-powersharing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[恢复北爱尔兰权力分享的协议取决于杰弗里·唐纳森爵士的支持，而这位北爱尔兰民主统一党领导人的突然辞职肯定会引发人们对这一安排的未来的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-29/donaldson-resignation-will-prompt-fresh-questions-for-dup-and-powersharing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 14:57:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和土耳其举行安全会谈以修复紧张关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/us-turkey-hold-security-talks-in-push-to-repair-strained-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和土耳其官员在安卡拉讨论了改善安全和能源关系的问题，这两个北约长期盟友寻求重建经受乌克兰和叙利亚战争考验的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/us-turkey-hold-security-talks-in-push-to-repair-strained-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 13:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯瞄准乌克兰水力发电厂，罗马尼亚发现碎片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/war-in-ukraine-romania-finds-fragments-from-russian-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰领导人表示，俄罗斯正试图破坏水力发电厂，而罗马尼亚在其与乌克兰边境附近发现了俄罗斯最近空袭造成的无人机碎片，这加剧了人们对克里姆林宫军队可能对北约成员国领土造成破坏的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/war-in-ukraine-romania-finds-fragments-from-russian-drones</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 12:11:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
